on your face.

67
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,450
Thank you.

68
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,220
Hey, Cao,

69
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,660
life is just beautiful.

70
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,290
