then Muhammad must go to the mountain.

74
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,370
But now?

75
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,930
The problem has rolled away
on its own!

76
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,700
Xiaoshang River is so far from here.

77
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,700
And yet Mu Dai had to personally

78
00:05:26,190 --> 00:05:27,850
deal with that Luo guy's mess.

79
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:29,850
If I'd been there,

80
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:31,250
I'd never have let her go alone.

81
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,490
At least someone
should've gone with her.

82
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:34,850
Unbelievable.

83
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:36,730
Poor thing.

84
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:47,780
Mr. Zhang,

85
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,020
have you ever been to Xiaoshang River?

86
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,050
No.

87
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,100
Good. You shouldn't.

88
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:54,100
Let me tell you,

89
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:57,100
that place is really dangerous.

90
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,370
No one should go there alone.

91
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,410
Oh? You've been?

92
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,170
Of course I have.

93
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:04,290
And that Luo Ren guy?

94
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,290
A holier-than-thou hypocrite.

95
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,900
Even Chubby

96
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,460
called him a stalker.

97
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,730
You'd trust someone like that?

98
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:11,810
Wait, really?

99
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:13,290
Maybe it's a misunderstanding.

100
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:13,980
Because...

101
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:16,020
Look,

102
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:18,100
Lady Dai is stubborn.

103
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,290
No phone call's bringing her back.

104
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,490
So what do you do?

105
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:23,340
Must send a brave and resourceful person

106
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,810
to assist her immediately.

107
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,140
Mr. Zhang,

108
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,930
Madam Hong entrusted her to you.

109
00:06:28,950 --> 00:06:30,540
If anything happens to her,

110
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,370
well,

111
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,220
you're responsible.

112
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,810
We do need to send someone reliable.

113
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,100
But who?

114
00:07:01,190 --> 00:07:03,140
Would you stop hovering around me?

115
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,410
You're making me dizzy.

116
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,660
I see what's going on here.

117
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,220
You're just mooching off Mr. Zhang

118
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,410
to dodge work

119
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:12,610
and live the easy life.

120
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:13,780
Look,

121
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,730
it's normal for workers
to want to slack off a bit.

122
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:18,050
Don't tell me you want to work.

123
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:21,250
Seriously,

124
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,140
are you going to see Mu Dai?

125
00:07:24,070 --> 00:07:24,730
Of course.

126
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:25,730
Why wouldn't I?

127
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,730
I'll just snap a few pics

128
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,780
and check in.

129
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:30,730
Hey,

130
00:07:31,310 --> 00:07:32,900
why don't you come with me?

131
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,900
Why would I?

132
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:36,020
Mr. Zhang's only covering
your food and lodging.

133
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,020
No perks for me.

134
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,610
You could just

135
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,410
freeload off me.

136
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,810
You just need to
pay your own travel costs.

137
00:07:42,830 --> 00:07:43,730
Oh, please.

138
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,780
You just don't want to go alone

139
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,730
and need a travel buddy.

140
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,460
That's a vicious misreading.

141
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:54,140
I have your best interests at heart.

142
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:55,100
Think about it.

143
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:56,780
You want to be her disciple, right?

144
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:59,170
If she won't come to you,

145
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:01,220
you go to her.

146
00:08:01,430 --> 00:08:03,140
If she runs away,

147
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,610
you chase her.

148
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:07,370
Traveling all the way to Xiaoshang River

149
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,810
shows devotion.

150
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:11,140
Even the coldest one would be moved.

151
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:14,900
Go on.

152
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:16,170
Alright.

153
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,410
If that wretched woman

154
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:19,140
ends up in trouble,

155
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:21,290
and you swoop in

156
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,730
to save her,

157
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:23,700
what would she do?

158
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:26,100
She'd beg you

159
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:27,100
like, "Cao Yanhua,

160
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,220
you're a great disciple."

161
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,460
Thirteen-Thousand,

162
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:33,820
you know, you come off as very annoying

163
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,250
when you're saying these things,

164
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:36,940
but I have to admit,

165
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:40,610
you're a genius.

166
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:42,980
Let's go.

167
00:09:23,180 --> 00:09:25,420
[Xiaoshang River Service Area]
[Motel]

168
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,610
You've got food all over your face.

169
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:45,610
Take your time.

170
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:55,850
Go eat.

171
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:57,010
I'll cover for you for a while.

172
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,060
You sure? You're still hurt.

173
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:02,010
Don't worry. I've rested well.

174
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,420
I'm mostly recovered.

175
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,530
Alright.

176
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:08,490
Your lips are chapped.

177
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,580
Haven't had enough water.

178
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:14,180
Don't lick them.

179
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:16,460
It'll only make it worse.

180
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:17,460
Drinking water won't help.

181
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:18,220
Is that so?

182
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:20,300
Do you have a lip balm?

183
00:10:20,980 --> 00:10:21,860
I left in a hurry.

184
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:30,580
Use mine.

185
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:31,660
I'll buy you one later.

186
00:10:31,660 --> 00:10:32,260
Thank you.

187
00:10:34,020 --> 00:10:34,780
Wait.

188
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:40,660
I don't mind.

189
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:51,860
Alright.

190
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:52,740
Thank you.

191
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:56,020
I'll go eat now.

192
00:11:13,180 --> 00:11:13,740
Mu Dai.

193
00:11:13,740 --> 00:11:14,460
Come here.

194
00:11:14,460 --> 00:11:15,580
Come and eat.

195
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:16,860
- Have a seat.
- Mr. Zheng.

196
00:11:17,380 --> 00:11:18,060
Thank you.

197
00:11:20,060 --> 00:11:20,620
Thank you.

198
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:22,420
You've helped us a lot these two days.

199
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,140
You have no idea

200
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:25,660
how chaotic it was before.

201
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,700
Luo Ren's upstairs.

202
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:29,940
He's watching Pingting eat.

203
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:31,540
They're so close.

204
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:33,940
Of course.

205
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:39,380
When Luo Ren first came
to the Luo family,

206
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:40,580
he was stubborn

207
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:41,780
and quiet.

208
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:42,860
But Pingting

209
00:11:43,380 --> 00:11:44,740
stuck to him like a shadow.

210
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:46,540
Followed him everywhere.

211
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:50,420
Here, have some soup.

212
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:51,420
Thank you, Mr. Zheng.

213
00:11:53,780 --> 00:11:54,580
Later,

214
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:56,700
Luo Ren left and no longer lived here.

215
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:57,620
But

216
00:11:58,100 --> 00:11:59,460
their bond stayed the same.

217
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:02,060
There was a time when his uncle and I

218
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,580
even tried to set them up.

219
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:05,540
Who would have thought

220
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:08,500
something like this would happen?

221
00:12:09,940 --> 00:12:11,180
Setting them up?

222
00:12:11,820 --> 00:12:13,700
But aren't they cousins?

223
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:16,140
Same surname, no blood relation.

224
00:12:18,100 --> 00:12:19,180
Calling them cousins

225
00:12:20,060 --> 00:12:22,100
was just out of habit.

226
00:12:22,420 --> 00:12:23,380
Just out of habit.

227
00:12:23,900 --> 00:12:24,980
Go on, eat.

228
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:42,580
What's wrong with you?

229
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:45,300
You're here to help, remember?

230
00:12:45,660 --> 00:12:46,900
Luo Ren and Pingting

231
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:49,020
are a perfect match.

232
00:12:49,220 --> 00:12:50,660
What's it to you?

233
00:12:50,940 --> 00:12:51,980
Look at you.

234
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:55,540
Just do your job

235
00:12:55,820 --> 00:12:57,220
and stop overthinking.

236
00:13:04,340 --> 00:13:05,860
We're out of drinks. Stop looking.

237
00:13:08,300 --> 00:13:09,900
That's a nice building.

238
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:10,540
Right?

239
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:11,940
Wait.

240
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:13,020
Hold on.

241
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:15,860
I think it's over there.

242
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:17,500
Keep going this way,
and we'll be off course.

243
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:19,700
See that arrow?

244
00:13:20,340 --> 00:13:20,820
Right?

245
00:13:20,820 --> 00:13:21,300
Yeah.

246
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:22,900
Any farther and we'll overshoot it.

247
00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:24,020
Let's go.

248
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:31,140
This is it.

249
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:33,180
It has to be here.

250
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:35,020
I'll check in with Mr. Zhang.

251
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:38,860
There isn't even a doorbell.

252
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:43,060
I can't see.

253
00:13:43,460 --> 00:13:44,260
Move a bit to the side.

254
00:13:45,420 --> 00:13:46,060
A bit more.

255
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:46,820
See anything?

256
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:47,660
I see something.

257
00:13:47,660 --> 00:13:49,460
Are we trespassing?

258
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:50,620
I haven't gone inside.

259
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:52,180
At most, it's peeking.

260
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,140
Fair point.

261
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:56,660
Any findings?

262
00:13:57,780 --> 00:13:58,780
I don't see anything.

263
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:00,180
Are you blind?

264
00:14:03,540 --> 00:14:05,620
There's a window boarded up with planks.

265
00:14:06,060 --> 00:14:06,980
Boarded up?

266
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:08,220
Yeah.

267
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,060
And between the cracks, I see a woman!

268
00:14:11,580 --> 00:14:12,700
Is that Mu Dai?

269
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:15,500
No.

270
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:16,580
Definitely not her.

271
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:19,700
Maybe she's one of those

272
00:14:19,700 --> 00:14:20,980
imprisoned girls

273
00:14:20,980 --> 00:14:21,900
from the movies?

274
00:14:22,980 --> 00:14:23,500
Get down now.

275
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,260
Let's call the police.

276
00:14:24,660 --> 00:14:25,900
No.

277
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:27,860
We haven't even gotten a clear look.

278
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,460
If this turns out to be nothing,

279
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:30,660
and Lady Dai is still inside,

280
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:31,660
you think you can ever be her disciple,

281
00:14:31,660 --> 00:14:32,700
and I can get away with this?

282
00:14:32,820 --> 00:14:33,700
That's true.

283
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:35,620
Keep observing, then.

284
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:37,260
Try to get some useful information.

285
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:39,660
I see that Hummer.

286
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:40,500
Duh, it's Luo Ren's.

287
00:14:41,580 --> 00:14:42,220
Mu Dai.

288
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,060
In a minute.

289
00:14:45,340 --> 00:14:46,060
What's wrong?

290
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:47,260
What else did you see?

291
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:49,780
